s://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthehollywoodeconomist.blogspot.com%2F2010%2F02%2Fif-you-are-producer-of-indie-movies.html&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSqwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=1de37406\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://thehollywoodeconomist.blogspot.com/2010/02/if-you-are-producer-of-indie-movies.html</a><br />\n<br />\nTo be sure, even before the phenomenal success of Avatar, the Big Six studios were shying away from smaller movies despite their potential profits. Consider, for example. the sad story told to me by one of the most successful indie producers in New York. In 2009, he brought a major studio a $20 million project packaged with a hot director and two stars. After running the numbers, the studio estimated that its potential box-office in America at $100 million, which would yield it, just from its 30% distribution fee and a locked-in output deal with HBO, a 100% profit on its investment. <strong>But it turned down the project. One of the studio's top executives told the producer, &quot;We don't do films that do not have a projected box-office of at least $150 million.&quot;</strong>"},{"pid":"1620a88934377f656ad91fb3e43838b584f65541","tid":2029829,"uid":167658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3f237c10f5f8658af6005d81fd8ee04f4db58966","tid":2029829,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e3817f0ce2e0474223f9fb5943e8da6314c2c524","tid":2029829,"uid":167658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e8c145c02d459433deccdce5e7f5581f35afa834","tid":2029829,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>1.語言</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢點先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n唔係英文片, 基本上就唔會打入世界主流"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"未睇，上流寄生族係英文片？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"贏奧斯卡, 都唔代表係主流.  Moonlight都明顯唔係主流電影.<br />\n<br />\n上流寄生族美國票房係五千萬美金. &nbsp;<br />\n但對美國studios而言, 一億美金美國票房先至係主流. &nbsp;美國studios忸而家通常都拒拍票房無機會超過一億美金